      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEDERAL CASH (4) lines up here off a comfortable win at this track after jumping from box 8 (29.09). Has a tricky draw to overcome and will need a clean break. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Form reads well for this. HARA'S GHOST (7) spotted a start but wound up strongly late and finished third and beaten 4 lengths (37.57) at this track in OPEN. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Overdue and gets his chance. TOMMY'S WHISKY (2) stretches out further in journey and is having his first try at the trip. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 5 lengths (22.09) at this track. Looks one of the chances. HARA'S HARPER (1) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
